raw %>% 
    count(headquarter) %>% 
    mutate(prop = n/sum(n)) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = reorder(headquarter, n), y = prop * 100)) +
               geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = .2, fill = "lightblue") + 
               geom_point(size = 3, col = "navyblue") +
               coord_flip() +
    geom_text (aes(label = paste(round(prop*100, 1), "%", sep='')), nudge_y = 3)+
    labs(x = " ", y = "%")
